body:
Items Added:
- Calibrated Pearl: allows you to teleport to any of your friends;
- Cracked Pearl: the single-use variation of Cracked Pearl.

Enchantments Added:
- Multidimensional: allows you to teleport to another dimension;
- Postmortem: saves your pearl slot similar to keepInventory rule.

Crafts:
- Calibrated Pearl: by right clicking with the vanilla ender pearl on a lodestone block;
- Cracked Pearl: by smelting in a furnace;

Compatable Enchantments:
- Mending;
- Multidimensional;
- Postmortem;
- Vanilla Unbreaking.
